Columns: 1;
                                                  ruled lines: 26;
                                                  written lines: 25; Uniform layout. Visible complete hard-point ruling. Hair side and flesh side of folios distinguishable. All books except Joel, Amos, Obadiah, Jonah and Nahum begin a new page. Judges, Samuel, Isaiah, Jeremiah, Hosea and Micah commence a new leaf.Hafṭarot are indicated in the margins by a later hand.Another hand has numbered the chapters with Hebrew letters and added the titles in the upper margin.
